(3, 1, 'Privacy Policy', '&lt;div class=&quot;policy&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;padding:10px 30px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;font-family: ''Freight Sans Bold'', ''lucida grande'',tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif !important;font-weight: normal !important;font-size: 23px;line-height: 120%; padding:10px 0; color:#333;border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc&quot;&gt;Privacy Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;All software, Facebook accounts, eBook, or other service purchased on the livelyservice.com website are done so in accordance with the following policy. By purchasing LivelyService products, you automatically abide these policies. LivelyService reserves the right to change or modify these policies with no prior notice.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;1. License Policy&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;A license is valid for a single computer used non-simultaneously by multiple people. If multiple people use the software simultaneously or on multiple computers, you must purchase a number of licenses equal to the number of users /computers who use the product or each user/computer must have a separate license.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;2. Limited Usage&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Our company provides subscription for FFAP service. Your subscription would be invalid after you cancel it.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;3. Modifications&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You are not authorized to make any necessary modification(s) to the product to fit your purposes. Redistribution of the software in full or any part of it is strictly prohibited.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;4. Unauthorized Use&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Software license information, eBook download link, and eBook unzip password can not be shared. Sharing or other methods which allow for multiple, simultaneous downloads or usage are strictly forbidden and may result in termination of your subscription.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;5. Assignability&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You may not sub-license, assign, or transfer your license to anyone else without prior written consent from LivelyService.com.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;6. Ownership&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;You may not claim intellectual or exclusive ownership to any of our products, modified or unmodified. All products are property of Livelyservice.com.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;7. Customer Information&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We will not sell, distribute or lease your personal information to third parties unless we have your permission or are required by law to do so. We may use your personal information to send you promotional information about third parties which we think you may find interesting if you tell us that you wish this to happen.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;8. Security&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We are committed to ensuring that your information is secure. In order to prevent unauthorized access or disclosure, we have put in place suitable physical, electronic and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect online. We are using secure payment gateway (PAYPAL) for all the transactions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;9. Privacy Questions&lt;/strong&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;If you have any other questions or concerns regarding any part of this privacy policy, please do not hesitate to contact us .We offer support via email, Yahoo, Skype, AIM and MSN.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;.policy{margin:0 auto;font-family: ''lucida grande'',tahoma,verdana,arial,sans-serif;font-size:12px;direction: ltr;white-space:normal; }\r\n.clearfix:after{clear:both;content:&quot;.&quot;;display:block;font-size:0;height:0;line-height:0;visibility:hidden}\r\n.clearfix{zoom:1}\r\na{color:#3b5998;cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none}\r\na:hover{text-decoration:underline}\r\np{margin:1em 0}\r\n.topborder{border-bottom: