(4, 1, 'About Us', '&lt;div style=&quot;padding:20px&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Welcome to Lively 24*7 Service VIP Member Area!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;As a facebook marketer, you must have been looking for a place to get all materials for facebook marketing and also can enjoy good customer service support there. Lively 24*7 Service can not only provide you with powerful software for facebook marketing, but also provide you with kinds of facebook accounts, including blank accounts as well as accounts with friends. You can also outsource some work to us to scale up your facebook marketing campaign and enhance competitiveness quickly.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lively 24*7 Service VIP Member Area is only available to Lively 24*7 Service VIP Members. In VIP member area, VIP members not only can enjoy shopping with great discount, but will be first to enjoy beta products or services.There could be secret products released and VIP members can use them in the VIP member area. What''s more, VIP members can enjoy better and faster customer support than regular customers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;We will try to add more and more service to the VIP member area. If you have any advices or questions, you can contact us by the following means:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Skype: livelyservice&lt;br /&gt;\r\nEmail: support@livelyservice.com&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n'),
(5, 1, 'Terms &amp; Conditions', '&lt;p&gt;1. There is no cost for you to join and keep in our VIP program. All your payments will be added into your balance.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. You need to load the initial Payment to join and keep the minimum balance to keep in the corresponding VIP level.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. You need to contact our 24*7 sales support team by skype(livelyservice) to get our best support for convenience.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. You can use your balance to buy any product in our sales pages (Except special offers) with the VIP discount.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. You can get tricks, methods, business idea and solution support from our different people basing on your VIP level.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Joining our Silver VIP or Gold VIP or aboveis a condition to apply for a Beta Product Tester, but not a privilege.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Joining our Gold VIP or above is a condition to apply for a Secret Product User, but not a privilege.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n8. We promise 100% money back without any condition for your balance. However, we will cut the free bonus you got.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n9. All Rights Reserved. By joining in our VIP Program is considered you have understood and agreeed on this policy.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n'),
