(36, 1, 19, 'Dragon Boat Festival Holidays Notice', '&lt;p&gt;We are sorry to notice you that we will be on Chinese Dragon Boat Festival holidays from June 22nd 4:00 PM to June 25th 8:00 AM (GMT 8). If you need to contact our support during the holidays, please feel free to email support@livelyservice.com. We will get back to you as soon as possible when we are back. Looking forward to your understanding and patience. Thanks. In addition, we are providing limited time special offers. For more details, please click special offer.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-06-20 13:09:35'),
