(43, 1, 19, 'Notice of Bugs in FFAP', '&lt;p&gt;Due to Facebook recent change, there are some bugs in FFAP as follows:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1) It can''t add friends / send messages to the new event guest in the Add/ Message Online Friends feature.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2) It can''t find any ID from accounts'' friends option in &quot;Find Targeted Friends&quot; feature.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nWe will try our best to fix the bugs as soon as possible to keep it working well. We apologize for any trouble with you. If you have any questions, please contact our 24*7 support team. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', 1, 0, '2012-07-13 14:58:55'),
