placed an order. According to the quantity of the accounts you ordered, we would arrange the delivery of the accounts timely. For small orders, we would send the accounts immediately. Basically, we would deliver the accounts within the estimated delivery time. Please allow some delay if something unexpected happens. If you haven''t received the accounts within EDT, you can send email to &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:orders@livelyservice.com&quot;&gt;orders@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt; to inquire your order statue.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con4&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;You could check your paypal Email for the accounts you bought. We would send the Email with the accounts as .facebook format in the attachment. Please follow the steps in the email to import the accounts into our FFA or FFAP program directly to check it. The cookies of the accounts would be saved to protect your accounts security. If all of the accounts are checked successfully, you can start to use your accounts. If the accounts failed to check before you use it, please refer to next step.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con5&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;Any question or trouble about your order, please just reply our delivery email directly. Our 24*7 order support team will give you an answer in the most timely mode.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. We guarantee to refund any order before it is processed basing on your refund requestion;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. We guarantee to send you the PVA which meets the specifications described in the above form;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. We guarantee to provide simcard life time free auto reverification service in FFA and FFAP;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. You should be responsible for using our PVA accounts without following our instructions;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. There is no refund or replacement policy for any order after it is processed.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	function woaicssq(num){\r\n\r\n	for(var id = 1;id&lt;=5;id++)\r\n\r\n	{\r\n\r\n	var MrJin=&quot;woaicss_con&quot;+id;\r\n\r\n	if(id==num)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;block&quot;;\r\n\r\n	else\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;none&quot;;\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n	if(num==1) \r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==2)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg2&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==3)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg3&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==4)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg4&quot;;\r\n	\r\n	if(num==5)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg5&quot;;\r\n\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n&lt;/script&gt;', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `lv_product_description` (`product_id`, `language_id`, `name`, `description`, `meta_description`, `meta_keyword`, `tag`) VALUES
(86, 1, 'Account with Niche Targeted Friends', '&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;.step_title_1{ padding:10px; font:bold 18px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333;}\r\n\r\n.step_title_2_a{ padding:10px 0 10px 0; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:18px; margin:0 0 10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #CCC; padding-bottom:20px;}\r\n\r\n.step_title_2_a .table_1{ border:1px solid #395a9d;}\r\n.step_title_2_a .table_1 tr td{ padding:7px 4px 7px 4px; border-bottom:1px solid #395a9d; border-right:1px solid #395a9d;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss {width:680px; height:300px; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title {width:680px; height:69px; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/btn_bg.png) no-repeat; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li {display:block; float:left; margin:0 2px 0 0; display:inline; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li a {display:block; width:130px; heigth:69px; color:#fff; cursor:pointer;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li a:hover {display:block; color:#f0f0f0; text-decoration:underline; cursor:pointer;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg1 {background-position:0 0;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg2 {background-position:0 -69px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg3 {background-position:0 -138px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg4 {background-position:0 -207px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg5 {background-position:0 -276px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con {display:block; width:680px; height:270px; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con ul {width:658px; height:250px; margin:12px auto; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:20px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li {width:658px; line-height:30px; margin:0 auto; white-space:nowrap; text-overflow:ellipsis; overflow: hidden; cursor:hand; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:20px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li a {color:#03c;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li a:hover {color:#069; text-decoration:underline;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy {width:438px; margin:10px auto; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy a {color:#f00;}\r\n\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy {width:438px; margin:10px auto; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy a {color:#f00;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con .wf{ padding:10px;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Description&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;Account with Niche Targeted Friends is a service to provide Facebook account with thousands of friends who are interested in one niche. At present we offer three targeted niches, &quot;Lose Weight&quot;, &quot;Make Money&quot; and &quot;Dating&quot;. These friends are 100% real and active FB users. There are small, medium and big three packages in total. The small package will go with 1000 friends, the medium one with 2000 friends and the big one with 4000 friends.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Overview Video&lt;a id=&quot;tipsm&quot; name=&quot;tipsm&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;tips_video&quot;&gt;&lt;object classid=&quot;clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; id=&quot;player&quot; name=&quot;player&quot; width=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/player.swf&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowscriptaccess&quot; value=&quot;always&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;flashvars&quot; value=&quot;file=http://content.screencast.com/users/Lively/folders/Livelyservice%20video%20%20(2011.12)/media/c61dec31-ef00-4916-bd19-7507c2edf14b/Account%20with%20Niche%20Targeted%20Friends.mp4&amp;amp;image=http://livelyservice.com/video/AccountwithNicheTargetedFriends.jpg&amp;amp;screencolor=000000&amp;amp;controlbar=over&quot; /&gt;&lt;embed allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; allowscriptaccess=&quot;always&quot; flashvars=&quot;file=http://content.screencast.com/users/Lively/folders/Livelyservice%20video%20%20(2011.12)/media/c61dec31-ef00-4916-bd19-7507c2edf14b/Account%20with%20Niche%20Targeted%20Friends.mp4&amp;amp;image=http://livelyservice.com/video/AccountwithNicheTargetedFriends.jpg&amp;amp;screencolor=000000&amp;amp;controlbar=over&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; id=&quot;player2&quot; name=&quot;player2&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/player.swf&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Discount and Delivery&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. We don''t provide discount for single account with niche targeted friends.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. If you buy multiple accounts with niche targeted friends but don''t allow mutual friends among them, we don''t provide discount either.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. If you buy multiple accounts with niche targeted friends and allow mutual friends among them, we will offer 50% discount for the other accounts except the first one. While customers need to pay with Wire Transfer or western Union if the order amount is more than &lt;strong style=&quot;color:#F00;&quot;&gt;$300&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. It usually takes us 14 days to finish the project for single account, but if something unexpected happened, we would need 5 more days to finish the project.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. If you buy multiple accounts with Niche targeted friends, we will need 4 more days for each account. For example, if you place an order of 5 accounts with niche targeted friends, we will need 14 days for the first account and 16 more days for the other 4 accounts, so we will take 30 days in total to finish the project.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Specification&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;table_1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;660&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;216&quot;&gt;Specification&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;150&quot;&gt;Small&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;150&quot;&gt;Medium&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;150&quot;&gt;Big&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;216&quot;&gt;Added Number&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;150&quot;&gt;5000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;150&quot;&gt;10000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; width=&quot;150&quot;&gt;20000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Friend Number&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;1000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;2000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;4000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Included Female &amp;amp; Male Friends&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/yes.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/yes.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/yes.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Friend Source&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Niche Targeted&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Niche Targeted&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Niche Targeted&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Account Type&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Personal Non-PVA&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Personal Non-PVA&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Personal Non-PVA&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Friend Source:&lt;/strong&gt; Add targeted friends according to the keywords related to your niche.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Account Type:&lt;/strong&gt; Means the kind of accounts will be used to add friends. And we select Personal Non-PVA account in our stock to add niche targeted friends.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Working Flow&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot; style=&quot; padding-left:0; padding-right:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss&quot; style=&quot;height:200px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot; id=&quot;woaicsstitle&quot; style=&quot; padding-left:0; margin-left:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(1)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(2)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(3)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(4)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(5)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con1&quot; style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;wf&quot; style=&quot;display:block;&quot;&gt;You should understand the introduction of the service before making an order. Please read all related information about Account with Niche Targeted Friends service first, which includes the description, specification, overview video, delivery and policy. If you need further explanation, you can turn to FAQ section for more information. There are some common questions in the FAQ, which you may come across frequently. Moreover, you can contact our Sales Support for help.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con2&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;wf&quot; style=&quot;display:block;&quot;&gt;You should have already made an conception on how the targeted friends should be before placing the order. If you have known about the details of this service, then you can choose your favorite specification and click &quot;buy now&quot; button to make an order. After the payment, please contact us with your detailed customized requirements. We will give you an estimated delivery time according to your project.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con3&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;wf&quot; style=&quot;display:block;&quot;&gt;We will process your order after getting notification of your order. It usually takes us 14 days to finish the project for single account, but if something unexpected happened, we would need 5 more days to finish the project. We will contact you as soon as we finish the order. Look forward to your understanding and patience.The account needs to be checked by FFA/FFAP to update the friends number, mobile number and other information.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con4&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;wf&quot; style=&quot;display:block;&quot;&gt;You could check your paypal Email for the accounts you bought. We would send the Email with the accounts as .facebook format in the attachment. Please follow the steps in the email to import the accounts into our FFA or FFAP program directly to check it. The cookies of the accounts would be saved to protect your accounts security. If all of the accounts are checked successfully, you can start to use your accounts. If the accounts failed to check before you use it, please refer to next step.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con5&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;wf&quot; style=&quot;display:block;&quot;&gt;Please follow the steps in the email to check the accounts as soon as you received the accounts. If you have any questions about the account or if the account is checked to be not working, please contact our &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:Orders@livelyservice.com&quot;&gt;Order Support Team&lt;/a&gt; for timely help, we will reply you as soon as possible.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Notice&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. The accounts are created based on Personal Non PVA specification.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. All the friends are real and active users on Facebook.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Please check the accounts as soon as we deliver the accounts.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. We offer rebates or give discount for your next order if the targeted account friends number is less than final number.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. Delivery time mainly confirms to the estimated time in the above table.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. You should be responsible for getting banned by facebook because of suspicious activities.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. We only refund full payment to customer who cancels the order before it is processed.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Placing any orders is considered that you have agreed on all the above service items.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	function woaicssq(num){\r\n\r\n	for(var id = 1;id&lt;=5;id++)\r\n\r\n	{\r\n\r\n	var MrJin=&quot;woaicss_con&quot;+id;\r\n\r\n	if(id==num)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;block&quot;;\r\n\r\n	else\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;none&quot;;\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n	if(num==1) \r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==2)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg2&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==3)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg3&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==4)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg4&quot;;\r\n	\r\n	if(num==5)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg5&quot;;\r\n\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n&lt;/script&gt;', '', '', ''),
(66, 1, 'Invitations for Real Likes', '&lt;p&gt;When the page is well created and there are well edited updates on the wall so that the page looks really attactive and active. Then you can start to get real active facebook users to the page. And the small package of 1,000 Invitations for Real Likes is just for page owners to test it before buying more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;The estimated delivery time of Invitations for Real Likes is mainly based on the quantity ordered. The invitations are often delivered gradually to the page. This is a kind of beta service.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n', '', '', ''),
