td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;2. Password&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/yes.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;3. Account Format&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;.Facebook&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td&gt;4. Account Language&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;English&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;&quot;.Facebook&quot;:&lt;/strong&gt; It''s the account format which we send to you, you''d better import the account to FFA/FFAP to check the account in a safe way.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Working Flow&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot; style=&quot; padding-left:0; padding-right:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss&quot; style=&quot;height:200px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot; id=&quot;woaicsstitle&quot; style=&quot; padding-left:0; margin-left:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(1)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(2)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(3)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(4)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(5)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con1&quot; style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;Before you make an order, please make sure you understand our unblock friend photo verification service, which includes the Description, Specification, Discount and Delivery, Notice and Policy. You could refer to corresponding part for more details. If you have any questions about the service, please feel free to contact our Support for further explanation.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con2&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;If you have learned about the details of the service, then you can click &quot;buy now&quot; button to make the order. After you click &quot;buy now&quot; button, you can change the quantity and then click &quot;check out&quot; button to pay for it. After paying, you need to give us the problem account: Please export the accounts as .facebook format and then send to our email &lt;a href=&quot;orders@livelyservice.com&quot;&gt;orders@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con3&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;We will start your project according to your detailed order information and try our best to unlock friend photo verification in the estimated delivery time. However, some accounts are not so easy to unlock, which may lead to a bit delay. If something unusual happens, we will send you an email to inform you immediately.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con4&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;When you get the account from us, please remove old accounts and check it on FFAP right away in the flollowing way:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n1) Open feature &quot;Manage Accounts&quot;--&amp;gt;Click &quot;Import&quot; button to import the .facebook file into FFAP&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2) Open feature &quot;Manage Proxies&quot;--&amp;gt;Click &quot;Import&quot; button to import your private proxies--&amp;gt;Click &quot;Assign&quot; button to assign proxies for your accounts (you can skip this step if you are not using proxies);&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3) Turn back to feature &quot;Manage Accounts&quot;--&amp;gt;Click &quot;Select All&quot;--&amp;gt;&quot;Start To&quot;--&amp;gt;Choose &quot;Bypass Login Problem&quot; to check&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con5&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;If you have any question, please feel free to contact us for support. The questions will include, but not be limited to the service you ordered, related services you are interested in, queries about operations and feedback. You can contact our sales support team for sales questions and contact our tech support team for tech problems.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Notice&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. Please send accounts to &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:orders@livelyservice.com&quot;&gt;orders@livelyservice.com&lt;/a&gt;;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. If you''ve assigned proxies to your accounts, please attach the proxies to us as well.But please provide us the&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;username and password of private proxies for the purposeof convenient operations, or we will use our US&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;located proxies to unlock your accounts.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. After you send the accounts to us to unlock them, please don''t use them until we finish and deliver the accounts&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;back to you. It will cause much more troubles or make the accounts get banned if you login the accounts on&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;your side when we are operating them at the same time.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. In the service, we can just try to unlock your accounts which get picture verification. If there is any other types&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;of roadblocks, we will try to bypass them if FFAP can achieve that. But we can''t assure to bypass them all.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;All we should do is to bypass the picture roadblock which you ask us to do. We won''t be responsible for&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;other types of roadblocks.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Please check accounts rightly with the Notice in the delivered mail after we send your accounts, and if the&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;accounts are operated by FFA or FFAP and encounter same roadblock within 24 hours after delivery, we&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;can solve it without fee. After 24 hours had passed, we are not responsible for accounts if they happen&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;some problems.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. We can''t guarantee all the accounts will be bypassed successfully.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. The money of the accounts whi