we can''t assure to bypass them all. All we should do is&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;to add a phone number to the accounts you ask us to do. We won''t be responsible for other types of roadblocks.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Please check accounts rightly with the Notice in the delivered mail after we send your accounts, and if the&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;accounts operate by FFA or FFAP encounter re-verification roadblock，please run bypass login problem&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;feature to unblock it.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. We will not process refund to orders which our product team has started.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. Once the order is made, please inform us timely if you want to make any change for the order.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Please check accounts rightly after we send you the email that we can solve your problem in time.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. We do not provide any refund or replacement for any reason after order is sent out.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Be sure to learn about all information of the service before you purchase. If you have any questions, please&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;contact us.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Placing any orders is considered that you have agreed on all the above service items.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	function woaicssq(num){\r\n\r\n	for(var id = 1;id&lt;=5;id++)\r\n\r\n	{\r\n\r\n	var MrJin=&quot;woaicss_con&quot;+id;\r\n\r\n	if(id==num)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;block&quot;;\r\n\r\n	else\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;none&quot;;\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n	if(num==1) \r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).classN