 style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;Before making an order, you need to read all relevant infomation of this service in this page, including the description of Account with GEO Targeted Friends service, specification, discount and delivery and policy as well. If there is something intangible, you can contact our Support for further explaination. We will consider that you have read all about this service if you have placed an order.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con2&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;We offer three kinds of accounts with geo targeted friends, small account with 1000 targeted friends, medium account with 2000 targeted friends, and big account with 4000 targeted friends. If you have known about the details of this service, then you can choose your favorite specification and click &quot;buy now&quot; button to make an order. After the payment, please contact us with the targeted country name that you want us to target the friends.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con3&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;We will process your order after receiving your payment and requirements. It usually takes 14 days to finish the project for one account, but if something unexpected happened, we may delay the delivery time in order to offer a better service. We will send the account with targeted friends from some certain specific country to your paypal email when it is finished. The account needs to be checked by FFA/FFAP to update the friends number, mobile number and other information.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con4&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;You could check your paypal Email for the accounts you bought. We would send the Email with the accounts as .facebook format in the attachment. Please follow the steps in the email to import the accounts into our FFA or FFAP program directly to check it. The cookies of the accounts would be saved to protect your accounts security. If all of the accounts are checked successfully, you can start to use your accounts. If the accounts failed to check before you use it, please refer to next step.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con5&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;Please follow the steps in the email to check the accounts as soon as you received the accounts. If you have any questions about the account or if the account is checked to be not working, please contact our &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:Orders@livelyservice.com&quot;&gt;Order Support Team&lt;/a&gt; for timely help, we will reply you as soon as possible.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Notice&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. We can only target friends from Europe and America country at present.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. The accounts are created based on Personal Non PVA specification.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. All the friends are real and active users on Facebook.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Please check the accounts as soon as you get the accounts.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. We offer rebates or give discount for your next order if the targeted account friends number is less than final number.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. Delivery time mainly confirms to the estimated time in the above table.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. You should be responsible for getting banned by facebook because of suspicious activities.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. We only refund full payment to customer who cancels the order before the project is started.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. Placing any orders is considered that you have agreed on all the above service items.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	function woaicssq(num){\r\n\r\n	for(var id = 1;id&lt;=5;id++)\r\n\r\n	{\r\n\r\n	var MrJin=&quot;woaicss_con&quot;+id;\r\n\r\n	if(id==num)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;block&quot;;\r\n\r\n	else\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;none&quot;;\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n	if(num==1) \r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==2)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg2&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==3)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg3&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==4)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg4&quot;;\r\n	\r\n	if(num==5)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg5&quot;;\r\n\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n&lt;/script&gt;', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `lv_product_description` (`product_id`, `language_id`, `name`, `description`, `meta_description`, `meta_keyword`, `tag`) VALUES
(88, 1, 'Account with Custom Targeted Friends', '&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;.step_title_1{ padding:10px; font:bold 18px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333;}\r\n\r\n.step_title_2_a{ padding:10px 0 10px 0; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:18px; margin:0 0 10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #CCC; padding-bottom:20px;}\r\n\r\n.step_title_2_a .table_1{ border:1px solid #395a9d;}\r\n.step_title_2_a .table_1 tr td{ padding:7px 4px 7px 4px; border-bottom:1px solid #395a9d; border-right:1px solid #395a9d;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss {width:680px; height:300px; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title {width:680px; height:69px; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/btn_bg.png) no-repeat; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li {display:block; float:left; margin:0 2px 0 0; display:inline; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li a {display:block; width:130px; heigth:69px; color:#fff; cursor:pointer;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li a:hover {display:block; color:#f0f0f0; text-decoration:underline; cursor:pointer;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg1 {background-position:0 0;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg2 {background-position:0 -69px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg3 {background-position:0 -138px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg4 {background-position:0 -207px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg5 {background-position:0 -276px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con {display:block; width:680px; height:270px; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con ul {width:658px; height:250px; margin:12px auto; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:20px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li {width:658px; line-height:30px; margin:0 auto; white-space:nowrap; text-overflow:ellipsis; overflow: hidden; cursor:hand; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:20px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li a {color:#03c;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li a:hover {color:#069; text-decoration:underline;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy {width:438px; margin:10px auto; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy a {color:#f00;}\r\n\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy {width:438px; margin:10px auto; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy a {color:#f00;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Description&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;Account with Custom Targeted friends service is to add targeted friends to any of your Facebook account according to your requirements. We select a personal Non-PVA account in our stock by random if there isn''t any specific requirements to add targeted friends. Or you can ask us to add targeted friends directly to any of your accounts on the basis of your specific demands.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nFor example, you can ask us to add a specific number of friends to your accounts. Or you can ask us to add a specific number of friends who are related to targeted keywords which are relevant to your accounts.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nIf we are requested to add friends by keywords, we will guarantee the number of friends as you request. While if we are requested to add friends by IDs or specific URLs provided by customers, we can''t guarantee the number of friends because we have to send friend requests to the IDs and it depends on how many IDs would accept friend requests. Usually, customers would explain their requirements in detail and we will start the project with our personal accounts directly.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThere are 3 packages in total, they are small, medium and big. The small package will go with 1000 friends, the medium one with 2000 friends and the big one with 4000 friends. Customers can buy any of them according to actual requirements.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Overview Video&lt;a id=&quot;tipsm&quot; name=&quot;tipsm&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;tips_video&quot;&gt;&lt;object classid=&quot;clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; id=&quot;player&quot; name=&quot;player&quot; width=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/player.swf&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowscriptaccess&quot; value=&quot;always&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;flashvars&quot; value=&quot;file=http://content.screencast.com/users/Lively/folders/Livelyservice%20video%20%20(2011.12)/media/2485d273-e19e-4d7d-9df6-c84fb7949e05/Account%20with%20Custom%20Targeted%20Friends%20Service.mp4&amp;amp;image=http://livelyservice.com/video/AccountwithCusomTargetedFriends.jpg&amp;amp;screencolor=000000&amp;amp;controlbar=over&quot; /&gt;&lt;embed allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; allowscriptaccess=&quot;always&quot; flashvars=&quot;file=http://content.screencast.com/users/Lively/folders/Livelyservice%20video%20%20(2011.12)/media/2485d273-e19e-4d7d-9df6-c84fb7949e05/Account%20with%20Custom%20Targeted%20Friends%20Service.mp4&amp;amp;image=http://livelyservice.com/video/AccountwithCusomTargetedFriends.jpg&amp;amp;screencolor=000000&amp;amp;controlbar=over&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; id=&quot;player2&quot; name=&quot;player2&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/player.swf&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Discount and Delivery&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1.&amp;nbsp; You will get discount for the custom targeted friend service corresponding to your VIP level.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. It usually takes us 14 days to finish the project for single account, but if something unexpected happened, we would need 5 more days to finish the project.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. If you buy multiple accounts with Niche targeted friends, we will need 4 more days for each account. For example, if you place an order of 5 accounts with niche targeted friends, we will need 14 days for the first account and 16 more days for the other 4 accounts, so we will take 30 days in total to finish the project.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_2.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Specification&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;table_1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;table border=&quot;0&quot; cellpadding=&quot;0&quot; cellspacing=&quot;0&quot; width=&quot;660&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;tbody&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;246&quot;&gt;Specification&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;140&quot;&gt;Small&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;140&quot;&gt;Medium&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot; bgcolor=&quot;#6d84b8&quot; style=&quot;color:#FFF;&quot; width=&quot;140&quot;&gt;Big&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Added Number&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;5000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;10000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;20000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Friend Number&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;1000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;2000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;4000&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Friend Source&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Custom&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Custom&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Custom&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n		&lt;tr&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Account Type&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Personal Non-PVA&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Personal Non-PVA&lt;/td&gt;\r\n			&lt;td align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;Personal Non-PVA&lt;/td&gt;\r\n		&lt;/tr&gt;\r\n	&lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Added Number:&lt;/strong&gt; Means the friend number which we will add for the account.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Friend Number:&lt;/strong&gt; Means the final friends number the account will get.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Friend Source:&lt;/strong&gt; Add targeted friends according to your requirement for the account.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;strong&gt;Account Type:&lt;/strong&gt; Means the kind of accounts will be used to add friends. And we select Personal Non-PVA account in our stock to add targeted friends.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_4.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Working Flow&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot; style=&quot; padding-left:0; padding-right:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss&quot; style=&quot;height:200px;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;ul class=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot; id=&quot;woaicsstitle&quot; style=&quot; padding-left:0; margin-left:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(1)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(2)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(3)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(4)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n	&lt;li&gt;&lt;a onclick=&quot;javascript:woaicssq(5)&quot; style=&quot;cursor:pointer; display:block; height:69px; width:130px;&quot;&gt; &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con1&quot; style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;First of all, you should try to understand the service which is quite different from other service. For the beginner of Facebook marketing, we highly suggest you learn it on Facebook first, so that you will know what kind of people you want to find. After that, please contact our Sales Support Team with your demands. We will be glad to help you if you have any questions about the service.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con2&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;You should have already made an conception on how the targeted friends should be before placing the order. If you have known about the details of this service, then you can choose your favorite specification and click &quot;buy now&quot; button to make an order. After the payment, please contact us with your detailed customized requirements. We will give you an estimated delivery time according to your project.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con3&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;Usually we will finish projects in 14 days and you can ask our support about the project''s progress. However, some delay may happen due to some uncertain factors. A notification emaill will be sent to apologize for the delay in delivery.We will send the account with *.facebook file to your Paypal email when we finish the project. The account needs to be checked by FFA/FFAP to update the friends number, mobile number and other information.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con4&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;You could check your paypal Email for the accounts you bought. We would send the Email with the accounts as .facebook format in the attachment. Please follow the steps in the email to import the accounts into our FFA or FFAP program directly to check it. The cookies of the accounts would be saved to protect your accounts security. If all of the accounts are checked successfully, you can start to use your accounts. If the accounts failed to check before you use it, please refer to next step.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;woaicss_con&quot; id=&quot;woaicss_con5&quot; style=&quot;display:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;display:block; padding-left:0; padding-top:12px;&quot;&gt;Please follow the steps in the email to check the accounts as soon as you received the accounts. If you have any questions about the account or if the account is checked to be not working, please contact our &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:Orders@livelyservice.com&quot;&gt;Order Support Team&lt;/a&gt; for timely help, we will reply you as soon as possible.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;Notice&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. The accounts are created based on Personal Non PVA specification.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. All the friends are real and active users on Facebook.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. Please check the accounts within 24 hours as soon as you get them.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. If you request to add friends by keywords, we offer rebates or give discount for your next order if the targeted&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;account friends number is less than final number.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. If you request to add friends by the IDs or URLs list you offer, we can''t guarantee the number of friends.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;We won''t offer any rebates or discount if the targeted account friends number is less than final number.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_5.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Policy&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;1. Delivery time mainly confirms to the estimated time in the above table.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n2. After the accounts are delivered over 24 hours, we are not responsible for accounts if they get some problems&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;later on.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n3. You should be responsible for getting banned by facebook because of suspicious activities.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n4. We only refund full payment to customer who cancels the order before it is started.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n5. Except for the above conditions, we don''t provide refund in any case.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n6. Be sure to understand the policy before you purchase. Any questions, be sure to contact us for better&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;understanding.&lt;br /&gt;\r\n7. Placing any orders is considered that you have agreed on all the above service items.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;script language=&quot;javascript&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	function woaicssq(num){\r\n\r\n	for(var id = 1;id&lt;=5;id++)\r\n\r\n	{\r\n\r\n	var MrJin=&quot;woaicss_con&quot;+id;\r\n\r\n	if(id==num)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;block&quot;;\r\n\r\n	else\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(MrJin).style.display=&quot;none&quot;;\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n	if(num==1) \r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg1&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==2)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg2&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==3)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg3&quot;;\r\n\r\n	if(num==4)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg4&quot;;\r\n	\r\n	if(num==5)\r\n\r\n	document.getElementById(&quot;woaicsstitle&quot;).className=&quot;woaicss_title woaicss_title_bg5&quot;;\r\n\r\n\r\n	}\r\n\r\n&lt;/script&gt;', '', '', '');
