(101, 1, '30 Days Action Plan', '&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;.step_title_1{ padding:10px; font:bold 18px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333;}\r\n\r\n.step_title_2_a{ padding:10px 0 10px 0; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:18px; margin:0 0 10px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #CCC; padding-bottom:20px;}\r\n\r\n.step_title_2_a .table_1{ border:1px solid #395a9d;}\r\n.step_title_2_a .table_1 tr td{ padding:7px 4px 7px 4px; border-bottom:1px solid #395a9d; border-right:1px solid #395a9d;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss {width:680px; height:300px; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title {width:680px; height:69px; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/btn_bg.png) no-repeat; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li {display:block; float:left; margin:0 2px 0 0; display:inline; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li a {display:block; width:130px; heigth:69px; color:#fff; cursor:pointer;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title li a:hover {display:block; color:#f0f0f0; text-decoration:underline; cursor:pointer;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg1 {background-position:0 0;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg2 {background-position:0 -69px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg3 {background-position:0 -138px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg4 {background-position:0 -207px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_title_bg5 {background-position:0 -276px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con {display:block; width:680px; height:270px; overflow:hidden;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con ul {width:658px; height:250px; margin:12px auto; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:20px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li {width:658px; line-height:30px; margin:0 auto; white-space:nowrap; text-overflow:ellipsis; overflow: hidden; cursor:hand; font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; line-height:20px;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li a {color:#03c;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_con li a:hover {color:#069; text-decoration:underline;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy {width:438px; margin:10px auto; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy a {color:#f00;}\r\n\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy {width:438px; margin:10px auto; text-align:center;}\r\n\r\n.woaicss_copy a {color:#f00;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_1.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Description&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;30 Days Action Plan is a practical e-book to guide you how to find and reach tons of target customers on Facebook within 30 days. If you want to start selling own product, or expand the business, 30 Days Action Plan is ready for you. In this plan, according to 30 Days Action Plan E-book and Schedule, it''s easy to operate step by step. There are examples and case studies in each step, showing by numerous screenshots, and the result assessment in each step is concluded according to our extensive research for this plan. With this e-book, you''ll learn to:&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Manage your Facebook time&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Understand the facebook rules of adding friends&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Figure out how to get targeted friends efficiently&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Get in front of more leads and prospects&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\n• Set up powerful facebook accounts with your target customers&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&lt;br /&gt;\r\nThe plan has targeted course for Beginner, Intermediate User and Advanced User. After completing 30 Days Action Plan, for the beginner, you''ll get an account with about 1000 friends; for the Intermediate user, you''ll have about 2000 friends; surprisingly, for the Advanced user, you will get more than 4000 friends.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_3.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Overview Video&lt;a id=&quot;tipsm&quot; name=&quot;tipsm&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;tips_video&quot;&gt;&lt;object classid=&quot;clsid:D27CDB6E-AE6D-11cf-96B8-444553540000&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; id=&quot;player&quot; name=&quot;player&quot; width=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;movie&quot; value=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/player.swf&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowfullscreen&quot; value=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;allowscriptaccess&quot; value=&quot;always&quot; /&gt;&lt;param name=&quot;flashvars&quot; value=&quot;file=http://content.screencast.com/users/Lively/folders/Livelyservice%20video%20%20(2011.12)/media/5ce35344-d5df-430a-acbb-1bc0af369157/30%20Days%20Action%20Plan.mp4&amp;amp;image=http://livelyservice.com/video/30DaysActionPlan.jpg&amp;amp;screencolor=000000&amp;amp;controlbar=over&quot; /&gt;&lt;embed allowfullscreen=&quot;true&quot; allowscriptaccess=&quot;always&quot; flashvars=&quot;file=http://content.screencast.com/users/Lively/folders/Livelyservice%20video%20%20(2011.12)/media/5ce35344-d5df-430a-acbb-1bc0af369157/30%20Days%20Action%20Plan.mp4&amp;amp;image=http://livelyservice.com/video/30DaysActionPlan.jpg&amp;amp;screencolor=000000&amp;amp;controlbar=over&quot; height=&quot;298&quot; id=&quot;player2&quot; name=&quot;player2&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/player.swf&quot; type=&quot;application/x-shockwave-flash&quot; width=&quot;396&quot;&gt;&lt;/embed&gt;&lt;/object&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_7.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Discount and Delivery&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2_a&quot;&gt;We don''t provide volume discounts. The estimated delivery time is within 24 hours.&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;h