t;&gt;.pageText_a{ padding-left:4px;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab1{ list-style:none; font: bold 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent:0;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab1x{ list-style:none; font: bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent:0; line-height:18px; color:#333;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab2{ list-style:none; font: bold 12px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#393; text-indent:0;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab3{ list-style:none; }\r\n.pageText_a h3{color:#333; margin:0; font: normal 16px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;  padding-top:5px; display:block; padding-bottom:5px; width:660px; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:underline;}\r\n.pageText_a h3 a{ color:#333; font:15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;}\r\n.pageText_a li{font: bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom:17px; display:block;  width:640px;  background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:1px;}\r\n.pageText_a ol{ display:block; margin:0 auto; padding:10px 0 0 18px; height:auto; padding-left:1px;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_1&quot; name=&quot;faq_1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_1&quot;&gt;1. Q: Why are male and female account so different in price? &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: The acceptance rate of male account is a bit lower than that of female account. It''s harder for male account to get a certain number of friends than female one, so we charge more for male account with friends.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_2&quot; name=&quot;faq_2&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_2&quot;&gt;2. Q: What kind of friends can you add to accounts?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: We can add friends based on three Niches we offered: &quot;Lose Weight&quot;, &quot;Make Money&quot; and &quot;Dating&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_3&quot; name=&quot;faq_3&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_3&quot;&gt;3. Q: What is a .facebook file?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: It is a file which includes all the account(s)’ information, for example: email, password, the number of friends, and the creation cookies which will protect the account(s)’ security and only can be used in FFAP or FFA.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_4&quot; name=&quot;faq_4&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_4&quot;&gt;4. Q: Can you add Niche Targeted Friends based on age/ gender?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry. We can only add friends based on niches in this service. If you want to custom the friends source, please refer to Account with Custom Targeted Friends:&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/account_with_custom_targeted_friends.html&quot;&gt;http://www.livelyservice.com/account_with_custom_targeted_friends.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_5&quot; name=&quot;faq_5&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_5&quot;&gt;5. Q: Are the friends real Facebook users?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Yes, the friends are real users active on Facebook.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_6&quot; name=&quot;faq_6&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_6&quot;&gt;6. Q: Can I also ask you to avoid adding the people that already got on my own profile?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry for that. We use suggest friends function to develop account. All friends we suggest to be from a huge real niche friends stock which has been build already.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_7&quot; name=&quot;faq_7&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_7&quot;&gt;7. Q: What do you need from me for the Niche Targeted Friends Service?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0px;&quot;&gt;You need to tell us which niche you are interested in, &quot;Lose Weight&quot;, &quot;Make Money&quot; or &quot;Dating&quot;; you can specify multiple niches in one account, but it is better to focus on one niche for one profile.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_8&quot; name=&quot;faq_8&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_8&quot;&gt;8. Q: Should I create a profile for you to add friends?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: In this service we will create a new profile and add the targeted friends for it, or add those friends for an existing account you provided.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_9&quot; name=&quot;faq_9&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_9&quot;&gt;9. Q: What’s the type or what’s the information of the targeted account’s profile will be&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; setting up?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: The basic information of the Targeted Profile is the same with the Personal Account we provide, check the details on this site: http://www.livelyservice.com/facebook_non_pva.html.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_10&quot; name=&quot;faq_10&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_10&quot;&gt;10. Q: Can you add the targeted friends for my own profile?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Yes. Please use FFAP to check your profile first, export the account with .facebook file and then send it to our support team. Please don''t use the account on your side before we complete and deliver your order, otherwise you take it at your own risk.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_11&quot; name=&quot;faq_11&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_11&quot;&gt;11. Q: Can I ask the targeted profile to make some customer settings when the account is&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; new created, such as the age, photo?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Yes. Please contact our Online Support Team and give us the details.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_12&quot; name=&quot;faq_12&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_12&quot;&gt;12. Q: I just paid the order, what should I do now?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Please contact our Online Support Team with your order information and which niche you want among &quot;Lose Weight&quot;, &quot;Make Money&quot; and &quot;Dating&quot;.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_13&quot; name=&quot;faq_13&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_13&quot;&gt;13. Q: What is timeframe for completion of this targeted account project?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: We will start the project as soon as possible after confirm your order, then it will take 10-15 days to complete the project for single account, If you buy multiple accounts in one order, we will need some more days for all accounts. In some case the timeframe may be delayed because of holidays, shortage of material and something unexpected happen, so please allow some delay then, thanks.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_14&quot; name=&quot;faq_14&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_14&quot;&gt;14. Q: Why can you send 20,000 friend requests if one account is limited to only 5000 friends&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; on Facebook?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: 5.000 is just the limited Friends’ number for one profile. As for the Friends Requests, there is no limit. Sent out 20,000 Friends Requests is to make sure one profile to get 4000 friends connected.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_15&quot; name=&quot;faq_15&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_15&quot;&gt;15. Q: If I ordered the Big Package, will I get the list of targeted 20000 friends when you&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; deliver it?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry, you won’t.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_16&quot; name=&quot;faq_16&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_16&quot;&gt;16. Q: Can you extract the emails of the friends from the targeted profile?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry, we can’t extract the emails of the friends from the targeted profile, while we can extract the friends’ IDs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_17&quot; name=&quot;faq_17&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_17&quot;&gt;17. Q: How much does the Niche Targeted Friends service cost?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: We offer 3 packages: Small Package ($50-$75), Medium ($100-$150), and Big Package （$200-$250). More details, please refer to this site: http://www.livelyservice.com/account_with_niche_targeted_friends.html&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_18&quot; name=&quot;faq_18&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_18&quot;&gt;18. Q: Can I get some discounts if I order more than one targeted profile?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: If you buy multiple accounts with same niche’s friends and allow mutual friends among them, we will offer 50% discount for the other accounts except the first one. However, if you prefer each account with a unique niche’s friends, there is no discount for multiple accounts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_19&quot; name=&quot;faq_19&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_19&quot;&gt;19. Q: What should I do if I want to change the targeted niche when the order is in progress?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry, we don’t accept to change the account’s niche when the order is in progress. However, if you want to add a new niche for the account, such as add &quot;Lose Weight&quot; niche to &quot;Dating&quot; niche’s account, we may implement it, please contact our Online Support Team if you think you’re ready to move on.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_20&quot; name=&quot;faq_20&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_20&quot;&gt;20. Q: Do you offer any guarantee of the actual friends’ number?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Yes, we promise the final friends number of account is around or equal to that we describe in specification.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_21&quot; name=&quot;faq_21&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_21&quot;&gt;21. Q: Why is my targeted account getting disabled from Facebook?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Facebook judges the account according to many aspects, there are many reasons why you are not able to access your account, such as overuse some feature, spam too much on Facebook, many people report the account etc. It is important to keep the targeted profile in FFA/FFAP and don’t overuse one feature for account secure.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_22&quot; name=&quot;faq_22&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_22&quot;&gt;22. Q: How to avoid the roadblock caused by the IP changing when I get the Targeted Accounts?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: When you get the accounts, please import the .facebook to Manage Accounts feature in FFAP/FFA--&amp;gt;Select the targeted account--&amp;gt; click &quot;Start To&quot;---&amp;gt;&quot;Bypass Login Problem&quot; to get the latest cookies of the account. This may protect the accounts security.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_23&quot; name=&quot;faq_23&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_23&quot;&gt;23. Q: Should I use proxy for the targeted accounts&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: If you manage more than 5 accounts then, yes, proxy service is recommended.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_24&quot; name=&quot;faq_24&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_24&quot;&gt;24. Q: When I receive the targeted profiles with friends from your service, can I change their&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; information such as the first name &amp;amp; pictures?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Yes, you can do that.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_25&quot; name=&quot;faq_25&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_25&quot;&gt;25. Q: Can I get a targeted profile with phone verification?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: All of the Targeted Profile is Non-PVA (No Phone Verification). We suggest you add your own phone number when you get the profiles.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_26&quot; name=&quot;faq_26&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;account_with_niche_targeted_friends_faq.html#faq_26&quot;&gt;26. Q: If I want a phone verified targeted profile, what’s the specification of the phone&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; number do you use? Can I request a US number?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry, we don’t offer this service when the order is in progress. All of the Targeted Profile is Non-PVA (No Phone Verification). . We suggest you add your own phone number when you get the profiles or &lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number.html&quot;&gt;Subscribe Mobile Phone Number&lt;/a&gt; from us.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;close&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 1, 0),
