t;&gt;.pageText_a{ padding-left:4px;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab1{ list-style:none; font: bold 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent:0;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab1x{ list-style:none; font: bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent:0; line-height:18px; color:#333;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab2{ list-style:none; font: bold 12px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#393; text-indent:0;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab3{ list-style:none; }\r\n.pageText_a h3{color:#333; margin:0; font: normal 16px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;  padding-top:5px; display:block; padding-bottom:5px; width:660px; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:underline;}\r\n.pageText_a h3 a{ color:#333; font:15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;}\r\n.pageText_a li{font: bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom:17px; display:block;  width:640px;  background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:1px;}\r\n.pageText_a ol{ display:block; margin:0 auto; padding:10px 0 0 18px; height:auto; padding-left:1px;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_1&quot; name=&quot;faq_1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_1&quot;&gt;1. Q: Are the accounts created by any proxies?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Yes, all the accounts are created by different US private proxies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_2&quot; name=&quot;faq_2&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_2&quot;&gt;2. Q: How long do the accounts created in your stock?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: All the accounts are at the age of 7 days at least, but if you want to buy aged accounts, please contact our sales support team to check for you.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_3&quot; name=&quot;faq_3&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_3&quot;&gt;3. Q: How old are the accounts in your stock?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: The birth year of all the accounts in our stock is from 1980 to 1990, we will send out accounts randomly without any requirement.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_4&quot; name=&quot;faq_4&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_4&quot;&gt;4. Q: What is a .facebook file?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: It is a file which created by the software automatically and includes all the information of the account(s)’, for example: Email, password, and the creation cookies which will protect the account(s)’ security and only can be used in.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_5&quot; name=&quot;faq_5&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_5&quot;&gt;5. Q: Is there any problem when I login the accounts with my IP or proxies which are different&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;with the created proxies?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: We can bypass all the kinds of roadblock for our accounts at present. If they are simple roadblock, FFA/FFAP can bypass the login problems for you. While if they are phone verification or friend''s phone verification, please contact our sales support team to help you.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_6&quot; name=&quot;faq_6&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_6&quot;&gt;6. Q: Do I need to use proxy for the Non PVA I bought?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: If you manage more than 10 accounts then yes, proxy is recommended. We recommended customers assign one proxy for 1-5 accounts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_7&quot; name=&quot;faq_7&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_7&quot;&gt;7. Q: Why the account creation cookies are important?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Browser cookie is an important factor for Facebook checking accounts status. If you login an account with new cookies under different IP or proxy, the accounts may get login problem. But it will be safe for you to change IP or proxy with same cookies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_8&quot; name=&quot;faq_8&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_8&quot;&gt;8. Q: If my Non-PVAs get roadblock when they are adding friends, can you bypass for me?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: We can bypass all the kinds of roadblock for our accounts at present. If they are simple roadblock, FFA/FFAP can bypass the login problems for you. While if they are phone verification or friend’s phone verification, please contact our support team to help you.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_9&quot; name=&quot;faq_9&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;non_pva_faq.html#faq_9&quot;&gt;9. Q: Can you help me create some custom Non-PVAs?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class