t;&gt;.pageText_a{ padding-left:4px;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab1{ list-style:none; font: bold 15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent:0;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab1x{ list-style:none; font: bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-indent:0; line-height:18px; color:#333;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab2{ list-style:none; font: bold 12px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#393; text-indent:0;}\r\n.pageText_a #tab3{ list-style:none; }\r\n.pageText_a h3{color:#333; margin:0; font: normal 16px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;  padding-top:5px; display:block; padding-bottom:5px; width:660px; cursor:pointer; text-decoration:underline;}\r\n.pageText_a h3 a{ color:#333; font:15px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;}\r\n.pageText_a li{font: bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding-bottom:17px; display:block;  width:640px;  background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:1px;}\r\n.pageText_a ol{ display:block; margin:0 auto; padding:10px 0 0 18px; height:auto; padding-left:1px;}\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_a&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_1&quot; name=&quot;faq_1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_1&quot;&gt;1. Q: How to phone verify accounts after payment?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Please export your accounts as .facebook formation with your order information to our order support team (orders@livelyservice.com), we will verify your account with a mobile phone number, and send you the account as .facebook file with new login cookies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_2&quot; name=&quot;faq_2&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_2&quot;&gt;2. Q: What’s the &quot;.facebook&quot; format in the specification form?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: The &quot;.facebook&quot; is one of account format in the software FFAP, it contains all the account’s information. Includes Email, Password, Proxy, Birthday, Sex, Phone, Added Friends list, Pending list, Status, Campaign, Security Question, Security Answer, Second Email and Cookies information.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_3&quot; name=&quot;faq_3&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_3&quot;&gt;3. Q: How to check accounts when I receive them from you?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Please follow the instructions in the email. If there is any problem with the accounts, please just reply the email directly, our order support team will check for you. While if you haven''t checked the accounts for a long time, account may caused by other problem with cookies expired. We are not responsible for that.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_4&quot; name=&quot;faq_4&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_4&quot;&gt;4. Q: what should I do when I get mobile phone re-verification roadblock?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Please start the fetaure &quot;Bypass Login Problem&quot; in FFA/FFAP to bypass for you automatically, it may take you sometime to bypass this kind of roadblock since we have to input the re-verification code manually in our side for your account. Or you can email our order support team with .facebook file format, let''s bypass it for you.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_5&quot; name=&quot;faq_5&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_5&quot;&gt;5. Q: How long will it take to phone verify my account?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: It depends on the quantity of the accounts, please check the table for reference.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_8&quot; name=&quot;faq_8&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_8&quot;&gt;6. Q: My account get another type of roadblock, can you solve it for free?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Sorry for that. We only help you to bypass phone re-verification roadblock for free if the account is bought or verified from us.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_9&quot; name=&quot;faq_9&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_9&quot;&gt;7. Q: How to continually use the phone number I ordered when my re-verification period is&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;expired?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: Please contact our sales support team with the phone number you want to use continually. You can continue to use this number after payment.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_10&quot; name=&quot;faq_10&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_10&quot;&gt;8. Q: Why Facebook require phone re-verification on accounts?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: It is because Facebook’s security system detected suspicious operations on your account, so it requires you to identity your accounts are real accounts or not.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_11&quot; name=&quot;faq_11&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_11&quot;&gt;9. Q: What is the different between mobile phone verification and mobile phone&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; re-verification service?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: &quot;Mobile phone verification&quot; means facebook asks you to input a new phone number to verify your account. It is usually happen on Non-PVA accounts.&quot;Mobile phone re-verification&quot; means facebook asks you to input the re-verification code from the original phone number which you used to verify it. It is usually happen on PVA accounts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_12&quot; name=&quot;faq_12&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;subscribe_mobile_phone_number_faq.html#faq_12&quot;&gt;10. Q: What possible reasons do you think may lead to phone re-verification? Can you give&lt;br /&gt;\r\n&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; me some advice to avoid meeting the block again?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;A: The following two reasons are probably to cause phone re-verification. &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Proxy problems. The unstable proxies may cause re-verification. If we use an unstable proxy, Facebook will detect that you login the account at some different places within a short time. So Facebook will send a warning message that requires for Mobile Phone Verification or Re-verification. Besides, when you manage too many accounts on one IP, Facebook may also detect this inappropriate operation. So we suggest you purchase stable private proxies, and assign one proxy for 1-5 accounts would be better. &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Abusing one feature on Facebook. Facebook will always monitor accounts’ operations. If you operate unreasonably, for example, you add too many friends or send too many messages in a short time, Facebook may know the account is not a real person, especially your account is new. You’d better not add too many friends for one account within short time. 9-11 friend requests and messages would be better for your accounts’ security.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;close&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n', 1, 0);
INSERT INTO `lv_product_tabpage` (`product_tabpage_id`, `product_id`, `language_id`, `title`, `content`, `status`, `sort`) VALUES
(99, 76, 1, 'Guide', '&lt;div class=&quot;con_right_3&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0; border-top:none;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;FAQ for Facebook FriendAdder Pro&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_b&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_1&quot; name=&quot;faq_1&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_1&quot;&gt;1. Q: Why the FFAP life-time license is not for sale?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;The marketing on facebook becomes more strictly now. We would like to limit the publication of our FFAP life-time license to maximize the effectiveness of the functions. While, you could subscribe our Monthly License if you would like to own the program within several months.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_3&quot; name=&quot;faq_3&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_3&quot;&gt;2. Q: If I order the Daily license or monthly license of FFAP, and I fill the &quot;Quantity&quot; as 3 when I go through the paypal payment, could I expect to receive 3 licenses?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;We would send you one license, with 3 days or months using authorizations rather than 3 licenses, one day or months permission. If you would like to have 3 licenses, you should make 3 orders respectively.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_4&quot; name=&quot;faq_4&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_4&quot;&gt;3. Q: If I place an order of Daily license, but I didn''t notice your Email of the register information until one or two days later, could you extend the license for one or two days correspondingly?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;If we check your license status is not been used for these days. We could allow an additional days extension.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_5&quot; name=&quot;faq_5&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_5&quot;&gt;4. Q: If any bugs occur during my usage of the license, could you extend the license?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;I am sorry. We couldn''t make any extension of the license when it got any bugs. Facebook keeps changing these days, we couldn''t promise the program works at any time. However, we always keep trace of the Facebook, we strive to update the program at the first time.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_6&quot; name=&quot;faq_6&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_6&quot;&gt;5. Q: Have you set any limitation of the 3 free trial time?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;It is possible that you could only collect 10000 friends ID and add 300 friends on the trial version. Meanwhile, it is recommend using one thread rather than multiple threads to run the features. For the other features, you could get full access to them.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;General Sections&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_b&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_7&quot; name=&quot;faq_7&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_7&quot;&gt;1. Q: Which operating system does your software support?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Three kinds of operating systems: Windows, Mac, and Linux are supported. That is, we offer different download packages for different operating systems, either you are on 32 bits or 64 bits.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_8&quot; name=&quot;faq_8&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_8&quot;&gt;2. Q: Why I cannot register the program successfully with my ID and SN?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Please make sure the following items: &lt;span style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:20px; display:block; margin-top:7px;&quot;&gt; Make sure you didn''t copy any space for the ID and SN;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:20px; display:block;&quot;&gt; Make sure you haven''t omit the &quot;==&quot; characters at the end of the SN;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:4px; height:20px; display:block;&quot;&gt; Make sure you have installed the right product, not others. FFAP programme is different from FFA programme.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_9&quot; name=&quot;faq_9&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_9&quot;&gt;3. Q: I have forgotten my license ID and SN. How can I regain it?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;If you''ve never formatted your computer, please find your ID&amp;amp;SN from the following path: C:\\ProgramFiles\\FacebookFriendAdder\\configuration\\.settings\\com.facebook.friendadder.launcher;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; If you''ve formatted your computer, please check you PayPal email for the license registration information sent from orders@livelyservce.com. Remember to check the spam box;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; The last way is to contact sales support team to solve this problem.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_10&quot; name=&quot;faq_10&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_10&quot;&gt;4. Q: If I would like to move the software to another computer, what should I do?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;One license only can be used on one computer, otherwise it will occur license error. Please follow the next steps to move your license to another computer: &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Backup your accounts file and license ID &amp;amp;SN information.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Uninstall the program from your old computer, then install it on your new computer.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Contact us to reset your license, then you can run the software well on your new computer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_11&quot; name=&quot;faq_11&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_11&quot;&gt;5. Q: There are following reasons may cause you get this error:&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Use one license on different computers, or open multiple copies of one license on the same computer;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Move your license to another computer;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Get a new update but left some old files in your computer.&lt;/span&gt; Then please contact our online support team to reset your license, it should work well after reset.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_12&quot; name=&quot;faq_12&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_12&quot;&gt;6. Q: How to update the program for Windows Vista and Windows 7 users&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;If you use &quot;Windows Vista&quot; or &quot;Windows 7&quot;, please try to follow the steps to get any updates. &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Open the following folder in your computer: C:\\Program Files\\Facebook FriendAdder Pro; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Right click on our program .exe file: FacebookFriendAdderPro.exe; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Select &quot;Run as Admin&quot; in the content menu to start the program; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;4s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/4sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; After started, it will find an update automatically, so please just go through the instruction to update the program. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_14&quot; name=&quot;faq_14&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_14&quot;&gt;7. Q: Why it prints the following error message on the console &quot;[Failed] 1536366334, Failed to get captcha code from you&quot;?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Please make sure you have marked the option&quot; use decaptcher service to bypass all captchas&quot; in the preference, and that you have input your correct decaptcher information. If it still doesn''t work for you, please login your decaptcher accounts to check whether decaptcher has updated the users'' decaptcher host. Please use your latest decaptcher host in our program to have a try.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_15&quot; name=&quot;faq_15&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_15&quot;&gt;8. Q: The running speed is too slow, so how can I improve the running speed?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Two methods to help you as following: &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Choose less interval time in the &quot;Interval&quot; options of the features respectively.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#333; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; height:auto; display:block; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Set the &quot;Http request global interval&quot; in the &quot;preferences&quot; features as you required.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_16&quot; name=&quot;faq_16&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_16&quot;&gt;9. Q: For some reason, I need to reinstall the program. However, I would like to keep my current parameter settings without change. What should I do?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;You could copy &quot;.settings&quot; file of the preview program to replace the new one of the new installed program. You could find the &quot;.settings&quot; file in the path of the program installed; it lies in the &quot;Configuration&quot; fold.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_17&quot; name=&quot;faq_17&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_17&quot;&gt;10. Q: I always get the license error when I restart the program, what should I do?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;The error maybe caused by the anti-virus program or firewall that installed in your pc. Please try to run our program as admin to open it.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_18&quot; name=&quot;faq_18&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_18&quot;&gt;11. Q: Did the program support any captcha service to auto bypass the captcha typing when it is required?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Yes, our program supports decaptcher service. The website is de-captcher.com. You could go to &quot;facebook-&amp;gt;&amp;gt;preference-&amp;gt;&amp;gt;Captcha&quot;, mark the option &quot;use decaptcher service to bypass all captchas&quot;, then fill your decaptcher information: decaptcher host, port, username and password. So that our program would auto use the decaptcher service to bypass the captcha.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_19&quot; name=&quot;faq_19&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_19&quot;&gt;12. Q: What''s the difference between login by livelybrowser and login by Mozzila browser? Will the program use the proxies that assign to the accounts to login Facebook?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Our program supports to login by livelybrowser and login by Mozzila browser at the same time. &quot;login by livelybrowser&quot; is based on your operating system browser. And if you choose to login the accounts by livelybrowser, then the account''s won''t login Facebook under the assigned proxies. However, if you choose to login by Mozilla browser, then it the program would auto login the accounts in facebook under the assigned proxies and its cookies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_20&quot; name=&quot;faq_20&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_20&quot;&gt;13. Q: Could I set different campaigns to run the different features at the same time to improve the effectiveness?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Yes, you could divide the accounts into different campaigns. Choose the targeted campaign to run any specific jobs at the same time. Our program supports 10 threads at most. and certainly, you need to assign unique proxies for the different accounts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_21&quot; name=&quot;faq_21&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_21&quot;&gt;14. Q: What''s the difference between FFA and FFAP?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;FFA is the regular software for you to manage thousands of facebook accounts, add friends and send messages. It only has 8 basic features. FFAP is the professional software for you to do facebook marketing. You can not only use it to manage thousands of facebook accounts, add friends and send messages, but also can use it to add targeted friends, send messages to targeted people, post updates, like and comment updates and much more other features. It has 22 features in total.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_22&quot; name=&quot;faq_22&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_22&quot;&gt;15. Q: It pops up a captcha window when running FFAP. Do I need to type the captcha manually?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Since our program can''t bypass the captcha automatically. You can choose to type captcha by yourself or buy decaptcher service to bypass it. Decaptcher ask for $2 for 1000 captchas. Please register an decaptcha account from this website: http://api.de-captcher.com/. Then Back to FFAP-&amp;gt; Prefrences -&amp;gt; Captcha -&amp;gt;Tick the option: Use Decaptcher service to bypass all captchas-&amp;gt;Input Decaptcher Host, Decaptcher Port, Decaptcher Username and Decaptcher Password-&amp;gt;click Ok to save. It will bypass captcha automatically when your account get captcha code next time.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;close&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Manage Accounts&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_b&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_23&quot; name=&quot;faq_23&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_23&quot;&gt;1. Q: What does it mean by the different highlighted accounts?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Black stands for Active accounts. Grey stands for Hidden accounts. Brown stands for Photo Verification. Light yellow stands for Photo ID Verification Purple stands for Phone Verification. Red stands for Disabled. Green stands for Login Failed. Pink stands for Phone Re-verification.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_24&quot; name=&quot;faq_24&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_24&quot;&gt;2. Q: What does the &quot;Pending&quot;, &quot;Rate&quot; and &quot;Added&quot; mean? &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Pending is the number of those who you have sent friend requests to but didn''t become your friends;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Added means how many friend requests you have sent by the program.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Rate refers to the friend requests acceptance rate, and the formula of computation is (Friends/ (Friends + Pending)) * 100%.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_25&quot; name=&quot;faq_25&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_25&quot;&gt;3. Q: Can I import as many accounts as I can to the program? Is there any limitation?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;You can import thousands of accounts, and there is no limit to the number.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_26&quot; name=&quot;faq_26&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_26&quot;&gt;4. Q: How to move one campaign to a different one? Fox example, move campaign A to campaign B?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Select all accounts in campaign A, then click button Campaign on the left. It will pop up a box where you can type campaign B and then all accounts will be moved into campaign B after you click OK.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_27&quot; name=&quot;faq_27&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_27&quot;&gt;5. Q: How do I just select some of my accounts and run them in the other features?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Select the targeted accounts first, and then right click on the selected accounts. There is an option called &quot;Start To&quot; which can help you start to run any feature as you like.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_28&quot; name=&quot;faq_28&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_28&quot;&gt;6. Q: Why I can''t import the accounts file into the program?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Please make sure the accounts'' format is correct in a .txt/ .CSV file;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please make sure you choose the corresponding file type when you &quot;import&quot; the accounts;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please make sure you never change anything in the *.facebook file before importing it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_29&quot; name=&quot;faq_29&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_29&quot;&gt;7. Q: How to deal with the issue: &quot;Login failed&quot;? &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/a.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;There are several possible reasons for the problem. Please run Bypass Login Problem feature on this account. It will print the log on the console. If it still get login failed error and you don''t know how to solve it, please send the log to our tech support team for further assistance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_31&quot; name=&quot;faq_31&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_31&quot;&gt;8. Q: I can login the account in the Browser manually, but why I can''t add the account in the program&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Please make sure you have input the correct email and password;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please make sure your Internet connection or proxy (if you are using proxy) is steady,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please clear your browser''s cookies and then login the account in the browser manually again to check whether it got some problems;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;4s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/4sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please login your account in the browser to see if your account have made some &quot;Account Settings&quot; to control your browsing and login security.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;5s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/5sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please clear your IE browser''s cookies and then try to add the account in the program again;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;6s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/6sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Please change the program''s useragent to your system default useragent and then have a try;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_32&quot; name=&quot;faq_32&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_32&quot;&gt;9. Q: When I finished updating the software, why all the accounts have disappeared? And how can I get back them? &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Sometimes, the anti-virus software will destroy the accounts file when you update the software, so you''d better back up one copy and close your anti-virus before you update the software. However, if the accounts'' file has been destroyed, you can not get them back.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_33&quot; name=&quot;faq_33&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_33&quot;&gt;10. Q: Why my friends'' number is not correct, it shows 1000 friends in the browser; while only 50 friends in the program? &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Please follow the steps to have a try: &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Select the account --&amp;gt;click &quot;Clear&quot; --&amp;gt; &quot;Friends Number&quot;--&amp;gt; run the account with the feature Check Account Information to check the account again;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; If you had assigned proxy to the account, the problem may also show when the proxy is not very steady or time out, so please use the default IP to check the account again.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_34&quot; name=&quot;faq_34&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_34&quot;&gt;11. Q: Any tips to make my accounts safer?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Assign a unique proxy for each account. Private proxies would be much better.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Use the spin format of the message. You''d better edit the message by yourself when adding friends. The default one is just an example, and many clients may use the message. So people may think you are spamming and report/block you when they receive this message. Your accounts will be banned if more than 10 people report you.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Pay attention to the content of update and message. If any URL is included, it''s better to use multiple redirection service. (Such as bit.ly, tiny URL)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;4s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/4sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Always keep the accounts in FFAP, since it will keep the cookies and other information of your accounts, so it will be safe for your accounts.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_35&quot; name=&quot;faq_35&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_35&quot;&gt;12. Q: What are the possible factors that would make the accounts be blocked?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;The following are the possible reasons for a blocked account: &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Change IP frequently;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Login account with different or without cookies; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Overuse some certain features; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;4s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/4sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Post lots of similar messages or the same URLs; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;5s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/5sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Send messages or URLs including any monitored keywords; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;6s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/6sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Too many people block you; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font:normal 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#000;&quot;&gt;7)&lt;/span&gt; Use a useragent which is not supported by facebook.com;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font:normal 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#000;&quot;&gt;8)&lt;/span&gt; Use a useragent which is monitored by facebook.com;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n	&lt;span style=&quot;font:normal 14px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color:#000;&quot;&gt;9)&lt;/span&gt; Too many pending friends;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_36&quot; name=&quot;faq_36&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_36&quot;&gt;13. Q: I double click the accounts to try to login Facebook inside the program, but it only stay on the homepage of Facebook, it doesn''t login successfully. Why&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;If you are at the first time run the accounts within our program or they aren''t been used for a long time, it may failed to login within the program. If so, please try to run the feature &quot;bypass login problem&quot; beforehand, then the account cookies would be saved in the program, so that you could double click the accounts to login successfully.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_37&quot; name=&quot;faq_37&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_37&quot;&gt;14. Q: I have hundreds of accounts in the &quot;Manage Accounts&quot; window, how could I find any specific accounts easily?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;You could search any specific accounts from hundreds of accounts by input the account Email on the right top combo box, the program would auto filter the right accounts for you easily.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_38&quot; name=&quot;faq_38&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_38&quot;&gt;15. Q: How to export a certain account if there are a lot of accounts in Manage Account feature?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Please input account email in campaign combo box, then it will filter automatically and only listed this accounts in manage account table. After that you can select this account to export and save it as the .facebook format.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_1&quot;&gt;&lt;img border=&quot;0&quot; src=&quot;http://www.livelyservice.com/images/title_6.jpg&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;Manage Proxies&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;step_title_2&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;pageText_b&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_39&quot; name=&quot;faq_39&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_39&quot;&gt;1. Q: How many types of proxies does the software support? What is the format when importing private proxies?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;The software supports proxies of HTTP, SOCKS4 and SOCKS5. &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;The format of private proxies of HTTP: username#password@proxyhost:proxyport.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;The proxies of socks 4 and socks 5: username#password@ProxyHost:Sockstype@ProxyPort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_40&quot; name=&quot;faq_40&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_40&quot;&gt;2. Q: How do I assign used proxies to my new accounts ?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Open &quot;Manage Proxies&quot; dialog --&amp;gt; Click &quot;Reuse Proxies&quot; button --&amp;gt; Click &quot;Assigning Proxies for Accounts&quot; --&amp;gt; it will assign used proxies for your accounts which haven''t been assigned proxies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_41&quot; name=&quot;faq_41&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_41&quot;&gt;3. Q: All the proxies are good when they are checked in Manage Proxies, but when I run other feature with the proxies, it failed?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt;Please click &quot;Check&quot; button on the left to check if the accounts meet any login problems.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Click &quot;Preferences&quot;--&amp;gt;Click &quot;Facebook&quot;--&amp;gt;Change the time range of &quot;Http read timeout&quot; more than 120, to keep the software have enough time to open the feature page.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_42&quot; name=&quot;faq_42&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_42&quot;&gt;4. Q: How to assign private proxies for my accounts? &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Please go through the following steps: &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Input these proxies in a text file (*.txt) as this format: Username#Password@proxyhost:proxyport, one proxy per line;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Open &quot;Manage Proxies&quot; feature, click &quot;Import&quot; button, select the 3rd option in Files of type, and find the corresponding text file;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Click &quot;Assigning Proxies for Accounts&quot;, it will delete the proxies from the dialog after assigning them for your accounts. Then you will find each account has been assigned one proxy in &quot;Manage Accounts&quot; dialog.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_43&quot; name=&quot;faq_43&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_43&quot;&gt;5. Q: How can I set up the Firefox proxy setting?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;Please follow the steps below: &lt;span class=&quot;1s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Open Firefox,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; Click &quot;Tools&quot; --&amp;gt; &quot;Options&quot; --&amp;gt; &quot;Advanced&quot; ---&amp;gt; &quot;Network&quot; Tab ---&amp;gt; &quot;Settings&quot; in Connection box.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;3s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/3sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; dis