service.com/images/1sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; If you login your account by browser, you may get a message that you need to identify friends photo. &lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;2s&quot; style=&quot;font:bold 11px Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; list-style:none; list-style-position:outside; background:url(http://www.livelyservice.com/images/2sp.jpg); background-repeat:no-repeat; padding-left:17px; display:block; padding-bottom:4px; padding-top:2px; margin-bottom:7px;&quot;&gt; If you manage your accounts in FFAP or FFA, you can use the feature Bypass Login Problems. The accounts in brown color mean that your accounts have got the Mobile Phone Verification roadblock.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_49&quot; name=&quot;faq_49&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_49&quot;&gt;2. Q: What should I upload for the login option?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;You need to prepare some good accounts with different proxies before running this feature. Export these accounts information as .facebook file and save it. Then click browser button to select this file. Program will login these accounts to collect all friends'' profile picture of the problem account.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;h3 class=&quot;textHead&quot;&gt;&lt;a id=&quot;faq_49&quot; name=&quot;faq_49&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;ffap_faq.html#faq_49&quot;&gt;3. Q: Can it bypass all the account which met friend photo roadblock? What kind of account can be easily bypassed?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;ol class=&quot;textBody1&quot;&gt;\r\n	&lt;li style=&quot;list-style:none; padding-top:0;&quot;&gt;It can bypass this roadblock for 90% accounts with full information. The account which was operated by our